# Docker & deploy (M7, M11)

- Pin base image tags; prefer Python 3.12+ for the Streamlit app.
- In Compose, set `OLLAMA_HOST=http://ollama:11434` (service name, not localhost).
- Self-host profile: `USE_DUMMY_GENERATOR=false`.
- Persist Ollama models via a named volume; document `ollama pull` as a one-time/init step.
- Do not bake secrets into images; use env files excluded from git.
- Expose Streamlit on 8501 internally; prefer Caddy/reverse proxy for public HTTPS.
- Healthcheck Ollama before app depends on it when possible.
